New Species of Parakiefferiella Thienemann, 1936 from South America (Chironomidae, Orthocladiinae)Parakiefferiella lagorum spec. nov. from central Chile is described and figured as male, female and pupa; P. hernandezi spec. nov. from south Chile and P. strixinorum spec. nov. from southeast Brazil as males and pupae; and P. wardorum spec. nov. from south Chile, as male only. In addition, an unassociated pupa from south Chile is described and figured. Keys to the Parakiefferiella males and pupae from South America are provided.